Package: splsleep
Title: Sleep EMA Diary Data Cleaning Pipeline
Version: 1.1.2
Authors@R: c(
    person("Cyra", "Sloblucyra", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "cyracaid@users.noreply.github.com")
  )
Description: A reproducible, auditable pipeline for cleaning sleep EMA diary data. Parses raw timestamps, detects and corrects temporal and duration errors through a human-in-the-loop CSV workflow, computes sleep metrics (TST, SOL, WASO, SE), validates self-reported durations against a schema-checked input contract, and generates QC visualizations.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
